UPDATE: Please check out the v2 of this map. It is the same map but a little larger in length for a better gameplay. - http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/62071

Hey, this is Kersh, I'm pretty new to mapping and this is my 3rd or 4th map. However, this is my first submission.

Not much to say but this is a pretty small map. It's an aim_ag map but it's recommended for GG. This is the final build of this map (I've done some testing with friends and bots) but I may add more onto it if people like it in a v2 of the map.

Anyways thanks for checking out my map and please leave any constructive criticism in the comments. :)
